<!-- About the Playground -->
<section id="about" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-800">What is the Playground?</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
      The Playground is a space where digital creators, entrepreneurs, and artists come together to experiment, collaborate, and create impact.
      It's more than just a place; it's a community built on innovation, openness, and mutual growth.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
      At the Playground, we don’t just imagine the future—we play it into existence. Here, play means flowing with possibility rather than being confined by structure. It’s the difference between thinking inside the box and moving with the stream.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6">
       <%= link_to t('global.menu.learn_more'), what_we_do_path, class: "text-green-700 font-semibold" %>
         
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Current Projects -->
<section id="projects" class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
